@startuml
title Diagrama de Sequência — Listar Vantagens (Catálogo do Aluno)

actor Aluno as A
participant "AlunoVantagensPage\n(Angular)" as Page
participant "ProfileService\n(Frontend)" as PSvc
participant "VantagemService\n(Frontend)" as FeSvc
participant "StudentProfileController" as PCtrl
participant "VantagemController" as Ctrl
participant "VantagemService\n(Backend)" as Svc
participant "VantagemRepository" as VRepo
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

A -> Page : abre catálogo de vantagens
activate Page

' Carrega saldo do aluno (para habilitar/desabilitar resgate)
Page -> PSvc : getStudentProfile(alunoId)
PSvc -> PCtrl : GET /api/students/{id}/profile
PCtrl --> PSvc : AlunoResponse{saldoMoedas}
PSvc --> Page : saldo

' Carrega catálogo de vantagens ativas
Page -> FeSvc : listarCatalogo()
FeSvc -> Ctrl : GET /api/vantagens
activate Ctrl
Ctrl -> Svc : listarTodas()
activate Svc
Svc -> VRepo : findAllByDeletedAtIsNull()
VRepo -> DB : SELECT vantagens ativas
DB --> VRepo : List<Vantagem>
VRepo --> Svc : List<Vantagem>
loop para cada vantagem
    Svc -> Svc : toResponse(vantagem)
end
Svc --> Ctrl : List<VantagemResponse>
deactivate Svc
Ctrl --> FeSvc : 200 OK + List<VantagemResponse>
deactivate Ctrl
FeSvc --> Page : vantagens
deactivate Page

Page -> Page : aplica filtros (empresa / custo máximo)
Page --> A : exibe catálogo com nome, descrição,\nfoto, custo e empresa

@enduml
